I verify verification email received in given email domain and from that email i parse the html url thru which new user can be verified
I navigate to the url fetched from email to validate the user
It should redirects to Success page
I input email data from excel sheet in email textbox
I input password data from excel sheet in password textbox
I click on Sign In button to login into an account
Finally once user has successfully been registered i will highlight that specific row in excel sheet to filter out
